But what about Wall Street=E2=80=99s love affair with Elon? Musk was alread=
y the world=E2=80=99s richest man before the election, aside from the few m=
onths when LVMH was on fire and
Bernard Arnault sat atop the standings. During that reign, Elon=E2=80=99s v=
ast wealth hovered around $250 billion, driven mostly by the market=E2=80=
=99s absurd enthusiasm for Tesla. (I get and even appreciate the devotion t=
