 part by optimism about Starlink=E2=80=99s and SpaceX=E2=80=99s likely expa=
nding role under Trump II=E2=80=94as well as an increase in Tesla=E2=80=99s=
 stock, which is up some 61 percent since November 6 alone. Is this too goo=
d to be true, or merely the beginning of a true wealth-distributing explosi=
on? (As ever, this is not investment advice.)

