 advice=E2=80=A6) Indeed, markets can stay irrational longer than most inve=
stors=E2=80=94even guys like Gabe Plotkin=E2=80=94can stay solvent, as Keyn=
es apocryphally noted about the dangerous art of
the short.=C2=A0

=C2=A0

While Musk loves to talk about how artificial intelligence and car-building=
 robots will transform Tesla before its competitors in the future catch on,=
 the carmaker=E2=80=99s present situation is challenging. There=E2=80=99s b=
een plenty of chatter about how their latest models aren=E2=80=99t nearly a=
