fall back to Earth. Short interest in the stock is some 81 million shares, =
or a mere 2.5 percent of the float. But shorting a stock such as Tesla, whi=
ch is so fundamentally and perversely detached from its financial performan=
ce, is a fool=E2=80=99s errand, and extremely risky. (Again, not investment=
